when do we use a four?
it was more clear with four
direct win,absolute defense and avoid oppent taking the point
all comes down to the simple statement:
never use any four unless you have to
and the reasons of "have to" are:
use four when you have vcf
use four when you worry the opponent might take that point instead
use a four if it is necessary for defense
do not use a four if you dont want to win
you cannot win in renju without a four
so, if you never use a four in the game, you can be sure you will never win
we all know how to find VCF
how about the second point: to use four because we worry that the opponent might take that point itself
